<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resolve Election Reminder</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body, p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, ul, ol, li {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #000000;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 10px auto;
      border: 1px solid #cccccc;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      height: 87px;
      background-color: #002347;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .header-content {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .logo {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 26px;
      width: auto;
    }
    .website-link {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #002347;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #ffffff;
      height: 161px;
    }
    .footer-top {
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      float: left;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-logo img {
      height: 13px;
      width: auto;
    }
    .footer-tagline {
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .footer-divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.1);
      margin: 10px 0;
      clear: both;
    }
    .footer-bottom {
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer-message {
      float: left;
      width: 164px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    .footer-copyright {
      float: right;
      font-size: 8px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    .action-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #002347;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dueipgl4k/image/upload/v1741814245/Frame_2147227052_cyssv9.png" alt="Resolve Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="website-link">
          https://resolve.vote/
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-content" style="padding: 20px;">
      {{#if reminderInterval}}
        <h2 style="padding: 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Urgent: Election Ending in {{reminderInterval}}!</h2>
      {{else}}
        <h2 style="padding: 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Reminder: Your Vote is Waiting. Act Now with Resolve!</h2>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px;">Hi {{voterName}},</p>
      
      {{#if reminderInterval}}
        <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">This is an urgent reminder that the election <strong>"{{electionTitle}}"</strong> will end in <strong>{{reminderInterval}}</strong>. Don't miss the chance to make your voice heard!</p>
      {{else}}
        <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">This is a friendly reminder that your election is still open! Don't miss the chance to make your voice heard.</p>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">Hurry now! Voting closes on: {{electionEndDate}} by {{electionEndTime}}.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;">
        <a href="{{electionLink}}" class="action-button">Vote Now</a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124; word-break: break-all;">{{electionLink}}</p>
      
      <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">Best regards,</p>
      <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">The Resolve Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-logo">
          <img src="https://example.com/resolve-logo.png" alt="Resolve Logo">
          <div class="footer-tagline">Secure Elections, <br> Trusted Results</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-divider"></div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <div class="footer-message">Start with Resolve: Create, manage, and monitor your elections effortlessly.</div>
        <div class="footer-copyright">Â© Resolve Rights Reserved 2025</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>